-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7.5 g","fat":"26.4 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"21.6 g","calories":"1496 kJ \/ 356 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, baking paper, slice tin (20 x 30 cm), baking tray (20 x 30 cm), palette knife, colander , oven, freezer","hintsAndTricks":["You can use raw, activated or roasted cashews in the filling.","<strong>Strawberry powder<\/strong>: Place 10 g freeze-dried strawberries into mixing bowl and blend <strong>7-10 sec\/speed 6,<\/strong> until a coarse or fine powder, as preferred. Use powder immediately or it will become sticky if stored for too long.","You may wish to store all frozen desserts in individual portions, as refreezing thawed leftovers can be a safety hazard."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","24h","15 portions"]}